+ WHAT THE FUCK ARE YOU LOOKING AT?

This is an aesthetic theme for team IN SPACE, NEMO CAN HEAR YOU SCREAM, featuring team captain [[*user Guaire]] and helmsman [[*user FlyPurgatorio]], who debuted Captain Nemo during the [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/pdcontest2025  Public Domain Contest]. The theme was created by engineer [[*user Fish^12]].

This theme is a [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:sigma-plus  Sigma Plus] theme and uses the [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:toggle-sidebar  Toggle Sidebar Component]. Aesthetically, the theme is retrofuturism and depends on the user to add their own stylings. 

To include this theme on your page, use the following code:

[[=]]
> [[include :scp-wiki:theme:retrofutura]]
[[/=]]

Besides that, there's not much else to this theme. I designed this theme with the intent of doing individual stylings per article, which more or less requires decent knowledge of CSS. I have some custom divs for your enjoyment, but don't rely on them too much.

I'll know if you do.

@@ @@

